## Time-Related Static Dependencies

| File | Line | Call | Count |
|------|------|------|-------|
| `Services/OrderProcessor.cs` | 21 | `DateTime.UtcNow` | 1 |
| `Services/OrderProcessor.cs` | 22 | `DateTime.UtcNow.AddDays(30)` | 1 |
